<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زَلْزَلَةَ السَّاعَةِ}</span> ... أَهْوَالَ القِيَامَةِ، وَاضْطِرَابَ الأَرْضِ يَوْمَهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَذْهَلُ}</span> ... تَغْفُلُ، وَتَنْشَغِلُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُرْضِعَةٍ}</span> ... الَّتِي أَلْقَمَتْ وَلِيدَهَا ثَدْيَهَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّرِيدٍ}</span> ... مُتَمَرِّدٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَوَلَّاهُ}</span> ... اتَّخَذَهُ وَلِيًّا وَتَبِعَهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَيْبٍ}</span> ... شَكٍّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَلَقَةٍ}</span> ... دَمٍ أَحْمَرَ غَلِيظٍ تَعَلَّقَ فِي الرَّحِمِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُّضْغَةٍ}</span> ... قِطْعَةِ لَحْمٍ صَغِيرَةٍ قَدْرَ مَا يُمْضَغُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُّخَلَّقَةٍ}</span> ... تَامَّةِ الخَلْقِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَشُدَّكُمْ}</span> ... وَقْتَ شَبَابِكُمْ، وَاكْتِمَالِ قُوَّتِكُمْ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَرْذَلِ الْعُمُرِ}</span> ... سِنِّ الهَرَمِ، وَضَعْفِ العَقْلِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{هَامِدَةً}</span> ... يَابِسَةً مَيِّتَةً.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{اهْتَزَّتْ}</span> ... تَحَرَّكَتْ بِالنَّبَاتِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَرَبَتْ}</span> ... اِرْتَفَعَتْ، وَزَادَتْ لِارْتِوَائِهَا.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِن كُلِّ زَوْجٍ}</span> ... مِنْ كُلِّ نَوْعٍ مِنْ أَنْوَاعِ النَّبَاتِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَهِيجٍ}</span> ... حَسَنٍ يَسُرُّ النَّاظِرِينَ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>